{
  "stem": "13524.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Lank, poorly developed-- no bust, no-- no figure.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was really inhibited.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I really was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was something that-- everybody was surprised that I dared to out up with something like that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So where did that come from?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we live in that area, that the language was used like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But not in school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not in front of the teachers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was a common word to use.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Even my children and grandchildren in Australia know that word.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's a lovely word.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, like, little 'botty'?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's a nice, sweet word-- not-- not so terrible.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But then, it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And certainly to tell that, and almost to tell the teacher.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because I included all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no, there were lots of Jewish girls.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But none of them stood up and said anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "None of them have taken part in the discussion.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I even expected the religious teacher, that he would participate in that problem and help me get back to school, because I felt I was totally provoked.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But, of course, his salary depended on the school management, and it was public school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he wouldn't have said anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was the general attitude that we have put up with anything and everything-- kept quiet.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Never-- to any antisemitic remark, we would never respond.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The procedure was to hide, to run away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If stones were thrown, you said, 'thank you' and you ran, and glad that the stone didn't hit you.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And if it did, too bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I wasn't brought up that way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My father was also six-footer-- six foot two, and I could see that he stood up for himself.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I  had a role model.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
